\subtree{\title{Scan targets at this tile}
\p{iPhone LiDAR scan of this tile should capture:}
\ol{
\li{Room geometry: walls, windows, door positions → \ref{bcf-0044} RoomPlan pipeline}
\li{Furniture placement: current objects → station reconfiguration plan}
\li{Light field: west window illumination pattern → screen glare avoidance}
\li{Cable routing: Cyton USB-C path from pegboard to screen}
}
\p{Ingest via \code{bb ingest-scan.clj <room.ply> iphone-lidar} in the scan workspace.}
}
